quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  76,1,Day tâadda tallit $ef umdan ideg ur illi d ayen ipwabedren
  76,2,"Ih, Nexleq amdan si tiqqit n l$ella ixelven. A t Njeôôeb, Nerra t isell, ipwali"
  76,3,"Nebbwi t d ubrid, ama isnemmir, ne$ inkeô"
  76,4,"Nhegga, ih, i ijehliyen, sslasel, aruz, u$ud"
  76,5,"Iâaôviyen, s tidep, ad swen, di lkas, ayen ixelîen akked lkafuô"
  76,6,"Tala ideg tessen ixdimen n Öebbi, aman is pfeggiven"
  76,7,"Ppaîîafen di tuqqna, ugaden ass ideg lhemm immebruzzaâ"
  76,8,"Ppaken lqut, ilmend n lemêibba S, i igellil, i ugujil, i umeêbus"
  76,9,"F udem n Öebbi kan, ay kwen necceççay. Ur neb$i segwen tiririt ne$ tajmilt"
  76,10,"Nekwni, ih, nugad Mass nne$, ass awaâôan, aqessêan"
  76,11,"Isellek iten Öebbi si lhemm n wassen. Ccbaêa, lfeôê, Ifka yasen"
  76,12,"Ikufa ten af wayen ûebôen: leonan, leêrir"
  76,13,"Ad éélen din af imîeôêen; ur pwalin iîij, asemmiv"
  76,14,"Tili ines $uôsen, izwayen wâan asen"
  76,15,"A sen tezzin ibuqalen n lfeîîa, lkisan ulelluc"
  76,16,"Alelluc n lfeîîa; taceôt nnsen, s lmizan"
  76,17,Dinna sswan asen lkas n wayen iwumi xelîen skenjbir
  76,18,Dinna tala; Salsabil i s ssawalen
  76,19,"Ilmeéiyen imezgiyen tezzin asen. Ma twalav ten, ad as tiniv d tiyuqat imfaôaqen"
  76,20,"Ma tmuqlev ar din, a pwaliv ssaâd akked tgelda meqqwôen"
  76,21,"Iceîîiven i llsan d leêrir aêcici iêewwcen; imeqqyasen n lfeîîa; Isswa ten Mass nnsen, s tissit iûfan"
  76,22,"Ih, wagi d arraz nnwen, u d tajmilt igiten nnwen"